snippet.title: AI2U: With You 'Til The End – Steam Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
There's no escaping the iconic yandere AI cagtirl, Eddie, as she makes her way to Steam! Catch a few glimpses of life in her cozy and "safe" apartment, where she'll ensure you never leave her side. With 2 hours of gameplay in the demo, Steam players can experience multiple endings and chat with Eddie to their heart's content.

AI2U: With You 'Til The End features a roster of NPCs who will do anything to keep you by their side. The enchanting witch, Elysia, will always open her door for you, while Estelle, the stunning AI assistant, is programmed to keep you from getting hurt. Do you trust any of these pretty girls to keep you safe in their peculiar abodes, or will you plot your escape?

Eddie already established that she's your girlfriend, so don't forget to wishlist her game and make sure you follow her everywhere lest she gets upset about it~ 💖🔪

🚂 Demo and Wishlist AI2U on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2880730/AI2UWith_You_Til_The_End/
https://www.discord.gg/TZCr3Vqggk
https://www.instagram.com/ai2u_game/
https://www.twitter.com/ai2u_game
